          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A precalibrated high resolution HPGe detector",
                "coupled coupled to a 4K-multichannel analyzer."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TRD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A strip of Lexan,the solid  state track detector",
                "was sealed in a polypropylene tube."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The overall error on the determined values",
                "would be the cumulative value  due to the errors in",
                "all the input parameters used in the determination of",
                "the absolute  yields. The determination of the number",
                "of fissions will have an error due to:",
                "   * the uncertainty associated with the track",
                "      registration efficiency,",
                "   * track density and",
                "   * the dilution factor.",
                "The determination of the fission product activities",
                "will have an error due to:",
                "   * the input parameters like peak area,",
                "   * nuclear data and",
                "   * the detector efficiency.",
                "The overall possible uncertainty with the determined",
                "value is within 5-6%."
              ]
            }
          ],
